        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Preventive Home Visit Act</b></p> <p>This bill expands Medicare coverage to include biennial preventive home visits, in which a qualified professional conducts a risk assessment of an individual's home and provides appropriate referrals for interventions or modifications to improve physical activity, fall prevention, and nutrition. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
